{"tid":711453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[小米痴左線] 雷軍豪言：小米估值應為騰訊乘蘋果","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T06:36:42.000Z","uid":42921,"like":12,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"451af3d1e99ccb98f62bc6658bb13afb8a1334de","tid":711453,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"雷軍豪言：小米估值應為騰訊乘蘋果<br />\n「小米是一家全球罕見的全能型公司，估值應為騰訊乘蘋果的估值。」6月21日，小米在香港香格里拉酒店召開投資者推介會，小米創始人雷軍對備受爭議的估值問題如此回應。<br />\n<br />\n自從小米籌備赴港上市以來，對於其估值的爭論和質疑從未停止。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，目前小米的估值在539億美元至698億美元之間，行使超額配售權後，估值為543億美元至703億美元，遠低於此前700億美元至1100億美元的估值區間，也低於高盛、摩根士丹利、摩根大通銀行、中信里昂證券、瑞信等機構給出800億至940億美元的估值。<br />\n<br />\n而市場的爭論點在於：小米到底是一家科技公司還是一家硬件公司？<br />\n<br />\n在今天的推介會上，雷軍重新用「新物種」定義了小米，他說，「過去一個星期我終於想明白了，小米是全球罕見的，同時能做電商、硬件、互聯網的全能型公司。」<br />\n<br />\n我不care小米是不是互聯網公司。很多人問我到底是給小米騰訊的估值還是蘋果的估值，我說我要騰訊乘蘋果的估值，因為小米是全能型的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/stock/ssgs/2018-06-21/detail-ihefphqm1083973.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2Fstock%2Fssgs%2F2018-06-21%2Fdetail-ihefphqm1083973.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=rKuEXMB5T1WbgDAVYwUu1SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=259f31c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/stock/ssgs/2018-06-21/detail-ihefphqm1083973.d.html?from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"6a3167380db67810ec1aa3ea3dfb7d2381194407","tid":711453,"uid":33714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a50929e76a20cb2a4e1c7e936d604bdbc9d7711","tid":711453,"uid":149902,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b627bc47e4f6e506ae7b67848365f90953c0bc6e","tid":711453,"uid":149902,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9c7ec1624c8dc3c5b6f405cbb100fa326e6ae60","tid":711453,"uid":42921,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"「好的公司靠利潤，偉大的公司靠人心。小米要做偉大的公司。」雷軍說道。<br />\n<br />\n笑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3bab47224419ecc3fc2b99b383155bef589e04","tid":711453,"uid":106363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"好期待招股反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789cf5304c285b0b9a91a75b016be642306fda01","tid":711453,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"騰訊係負數？"},{"pid":"6567ae2dc630afd7126e888f943990013a930d11","tid":711453,"uid":96728,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"個名都叫雷軍，仲信？"},{"pid":"cc2dac94f58b8f628f9bf5813ad136929c73afd0","tid":711453,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"成間公司冇技術可言, 一味靠抄"},{"pid":"df3bef39b82e349f6863b84719f9ba64ae4846d9","tid":711453,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba3bab47224419ecc3fc2b99b383155bef589e04","tid":711453,"uid":106363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"好期待招股反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"好多港豬送錢俾小米洗"},{"pid":"1e05c6432906f05a3d89755227b74c1cfa06b882","tid":711453,"uid":44454,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"騰訊4萬億，蘋果7.5萬億<br />\n4000000000000 x 7500000000000<br />\n小米估值：30000000000000000000000000元"},{"pid":"dffd71fef80df9ef6a5872ffb77252af5a825303","tid":711453,"uid":13663,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"